data.description: Spacious 4 bedrooms plus loft in the new gated Cerrada Lincoln Crossing subdivision! Situated on a private corner lot at back of community near  bike and walking trails. Steps to the community playground and access to the clubhouse which offers multiple pools, gym, sports courts and more. Owned solar panels, electrical upgrades, TONS of storage with oversized closets, overhead garage storage, and spacious kitchen pantry. Beautiful tile throughout lower level with modern kitchen featuring stainless appliances, subway tile backsplash and granite counters. Upstairs laundry tucked away off the loft, spacious owners suite with generous walk-in closet. Low Maintenance backyard with turf. OWNED SOLAR. HOA includes internet!
